    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cooperate with a friend to overcome obstacles using a grappling hook and an air gun!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012760/extras/b828813e31c679dff94b2cf20dcb930f.avif?t=1743064286\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012760/extras_big/b828813e31c679dff94b2cf20dcb930f.avif?t=1743064286 width=800 height=388 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In a mysterious <strong>super lab</strong> managed by an enigmatic robot, you and your <u>friend</u> (probably) have become <u>voluntary</u> test subjects (probably).<br>With an <strong>air gun</strong> and a <strong>grappling hook</strong>, you must work together to navigate the robot’s challenging obstacle courses!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use each character’s unique abilities to overcome tricky situations and enjoy a <strong>fun, lighthearted co-op platforming experience!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>2-Player Co-op</strong> – Team up with a friend to solve puzzles and conquer obstacles!<br>⚙️ <strong>Dynamic Physics-Based Interactions</strong> – Manipulate objects, characters, and the environment freely!<br>🧩 <strong>Casual yet Engaging Platforming &amp; Puzzles</strong> – A balanced difficulty for stress-free enjoyment!<br>🐣 <strong>Adorable and Unique Characters &amp; Objects</strong> – A charming world that brings a smile to your face!<br>😆 <strong>Dark Humor with a Comedic Twist</strong> – Silly yet strangely relatable moments!<br>🔄 <strong>Creative Physics-Based Gameplay</strong> – Utilize each character’s abilities in inventive ways!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Creative Character Abilities with Physics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012760/extras/71da8545e3d8560c62ed3ef0dedad6dc.poster.avif?t=1743064286\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012760/extras/71da8545e3d8560c62ed3ef0dedad6dc.webm?t=1743064286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012760/extras/71da8545e3d8560c62ed3ef0dedad6dc.mp4?t=1743064286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leverage each character’s unique skills for innovative, physics-driven gameplay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Interact with Various Objects!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012760/extras/b8293ec2b1b8cf921713646a430f8fa4.poster.avif?t=1743064286\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012760/extras/b8293ec2b1b8cf921713646a430f8fa4.webm?t=1743064286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012760/extras/b8293ec2b1b8cf921713646a430f8fa4.mp4?t=1743064286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use diverse objects scattered throughout the stages to clear obstacles and progress!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >...And stay tuned for <strong>even more features and content in future updates!</strong></h2>",
